snippet.title: Little Witch Nobeta - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out gameplay in this trailer for the 3D action shooter game Little Witch Nobeta and watch as Nobeta takes on creepy creatures using spells and close-combat attacks as she explores a mysterious castle. 

Little Witch Nobeta will be available on PlayStation 4 and Nintendo Switch in Spring 2023 in North America and Europe.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
